        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我能住苦聖諦。",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565b13_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』是菩薩摩訶薩我、我所執之所擾亂住苦聖諦故，遂起高心不能迴向一切智智。",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565b15_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩住集、滅、道聖諦時，若作是念：",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565b16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我能住集、滅、道聖諦。",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565b17_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』是菩薩摩訶薩我、我所執之所擾亂住集、滅、道聖諦故，遂起高心不能迴向一切智智。",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565b19_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565b20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩修四靜慮時，若作是念：",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565b20_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我能修四靜慮。",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565b21_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』是菩薩摩訶薩我、我所執之所擾亂修四靜慮故，遂起高心不能迴向一切智智。",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565b23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩修四無量、四無色定時，若作是念：",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565b24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我能修四無量、四無色定。",
