    {
        "source_sentence": "』是菩薩摩訶薩我、我所執之所擾亂修八解脫故，遂起高心不能迴向一切智智。",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565c01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩修八勝處、九次第定、十遍處時，若作是念：",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565c02_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我能修八勝處、九次第定、十遍處。",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565c03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』是菩薩摩訶薩我、我所執之所擾亂修八勝處、九次第定、十遍處故，遂起高心不能迴向一切智智。",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565c05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565c05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩修四念住時，若作是念：",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565c06_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我能修四念住。",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565c06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』是菩薩摩訶薩我、我所執之所擾亂修四念住故，遂起高心不能迴向一切智智。",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565c08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩修四正斷、四神足、五根、五力、七等覺支、八聖道支時，若作是念：",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565c10_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我能修四正斷、四神足、五根、五力、七等覺支、八聖道支。",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565c11_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』是菩薩摩訶薩我、我所執之所擾亂修四正斷、四神足、五根、五力、七等覺支、八聖道支故，遂起高心不能迴向一切智智。",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565c14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565c14_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩修空解脫門時，若作是念：",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565c15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我能修空解脫門。",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565c15_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』是菩薩摩訶薩我、我所執之所擾亂修空解脫門故，遂起高心不能迴向一切智智。",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565c17_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩修無相、無願解脫門時，若作是念：",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565c18_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我能修無相、無願解脫門。",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565c19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』是菩薩摩訶薩我、我所執之所擾亂修無相、無願解脫門故，遂起高心不能迴向一切智智。",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565c21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565c21_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩修五眼時，若作是念：",
        "from": "T05n0220a_102:0565c22_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我能修五眼。",
